tracing: kprobe: Fix memory leak in test_gen_kprobe/kretprobe_cmd()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.78 by commit d1b6a8e3414aeaa0985139180c145d2d0fbd2a49, it was introduced in version v5.6 by commit 64836248dda20c8e7427b493f7e06d9bf8f58850. For more details please see the references link.
